{"tid":2221015,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"疫情下水貨客消失 店舖紛執笠  上水藥房街業主「死充」拒減租","createTime":"2020-09-28T05:32:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T05:46:13.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"aca4073c3cd5ef8eb8e7b46e8f856cbf3e49f137","tid":2221015,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:32:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200928/PFEY74PZQ5GMFKPKP4UZOUGRAM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200928%2FPFEY74PZQ5GMFKPKP4UZOUGRAM%2F&d=Wx0cKZaQlto0GELw8F4hIXRNzM9MViFDfs2457H6WAQ%3D&h=94832caf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200928%2FPFEY74PZQ5GMFKPKP4UZOUGRAM%2F&h=ce19b11f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200928/PFEY74PZQ5GMFKPKP4UZOUGRAM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n疫情下水貨客消失 店舖紛執笠 <br />\n上水藥房街業主「死充」拒減租<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/mnKedT_wBbzqD9I0XBdADogPq6Q=/1221x763/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UVITYJ5N2RC3DMMV32GQLJ236E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FmnKedT_wBbzqD9I0XBdADogPq6Q%3D%2F1221x763%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUVITYJ5N2RC3DMMV32GQLJ236E.jpg&h=daf79d69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■疫情下水貨客絕迹，街坊可在上水新康街一帶從容步行。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】上水過往受內地自由行及水貨客帶動，龍琛路、新康街及符興街一帶「藥房街」，藥房、化妝品店、兌換店等遍地開花；惟疫情下水貨客銷聲匿迹，連帶街頭不少店舖已落閘或結業。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：藥妝店逆市租元朗舖<br />\n<br />\n本報記者日前到上水一帶視察，原本被自由行旅客、水貨客佔據的街道水盡鵝飛，新康街至少15間前身為藥房及化妝品店的地舖，不是倒閉及在鐵閘貼上招租廣告，就是拉閘未有開門做生意。以新祥街為例，短短50米已有6至10間店舖沒營業，部份店舖閘前貼滿招租廣告；新功街亦有約五成店舖無開門。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PuybaQkGvZrodlHrIYDrwybSm_o=/665x484/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UGIVAMK2NNHGBAHGDDCIU5D43E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPuybaQkGvZrodlHrIYDrwybSm_o%3D%2F665x484%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUGIVAMK2NNHGBAHGDDCIU5D43E.jpg&h=10f2a60f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■不少地舖已沒營業，並在閘前貼滿招租廣告。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n找換店：生意大跌逾九<br />\n<br />\n有街坊透露，該批藥房經營者不少為內地人，部份商舖在農曆新年後便再無開門營業。。。。。。。。。。。。。有已落閘藥妝店員工稱，年初起上水街客幾乎絕迹，加上公司接連裁員，「十個員工炒咗七個」，故現時只向內地人提供網購，透過微信落單，便可將貨物寄返內地。<br />\n<br />\n有找換店負責人表示，上水街上約有六成兌換店為內地人經營，疫情下店主難以往返中港兩地，惟有關門大吉；目前找換店生意，由去年同期月賺數十萬元，大跌超過九成。<br />\n<br />\n然而地產代理梁先生表示，即使受逆權運動及武漢肺炎疫情夾擊，租客減少，上水一帶有地舖租金竟然「硬淨」。市場消息指出，新康街現時呎租仍可媲美尖沙嘴、銅鑼灣等一線地舖，其中67號的1,200方呎地舖連8,909方呎閣樓，以月租55萬元租出，平均呎租約131元。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。，「𠵱家可能冇水貨客、冇內地客，但疫情總有完結一日；啲業主仍然企硬呢個市價，寧願間舖吉咗都唔減租」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/YHdr4qlXbYcTufPlKR9-YDO3gDo=/946x704/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JUOLVTUCU5HXBLJWUODYEGLSTM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYHdr4qlXbYcTufPlKR9-YDO3gDo%3D%2F946x704%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJUOLVTUCU5HXBLJWUODYEGLSTM.jpg&h=afb64182&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■昔日自由行及水貨客充斥上水街頭的畫面不再。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n業主博疫情後藥房回歸<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。，「都可以話班業主係『扮勁』、『打腫塊面死充』」。。。。。。。。。。，「藥妝店先租得起嗰啲價錢，其他租戶根本懶得講價，寧願丟空企硬」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gOcgvR2i1S2R_qUundZfToDwe0k=/950x609/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RNAXOSGUNNGG3HDB6U6HCIWYIE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgOcgvR2i1S2R_qUundZfToDwe0k%3D%2F950x609%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRNAXOSGUNNGG3HDB6U6HCIWYIE.gif&h=37f40819&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0000fee3a523094c7394495c2b1e62502941aa6","tid":2221015,"uid":134474,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:39:11.000Z","msg":"以為可以食肥肉，可惜呢種經濟只係曇花一現"},{"pid":"80693708a5923563e41974d0d3cd40d2cc97f6fc","tid":2221015,"uid":2054,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:40:04.000Z","msg":"企硬咪撚縮呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a325e7c9442d3ee74d7f3207998da2ac32680b4","tid":2221015,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:40:47.000Z","msg":"賤種 vs 賤種<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5483cc294ee533fd0803c4465d8e58b8bb6bc2d","tid":2221015,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:40:57.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">業主圖博疫情快過、藥妝店等租客能加快回歸。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n弱智 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11830b8f2a783845e5c5302658d26f5f4bed8a5","tid":2221015,"uid":52594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:42:08.000Z","msg":"認為要企硬加租，政府帶領下，經濟會再出發。<br />\n先到先得"},{"pid":"a73cf6fb4f7bad55280f7bb6acd0e3cef4fd9997","tid":2221015,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:43:12.000Z","msg":"日本拉麵店點樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4dd162a624bdb00f25184948300a1bc285e6f4","tid":2221015,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:44:02.000Z","msg":"東亞病夫專門店我冇興趣，執左話之你啦"},{"pid":"74ab3ff7145fd47cb72ca8c0d7e1e26409714e76","tid":2221015,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0000fee3a523094c7394495c2b1e62502941aa6","tid":2221015,"uid":134474,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:39:11.000Z","msg":"以為可以食肥肉，可惜呢種經濟只係曇花一現"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:45:45.000Z","msg":"同吸冰毒一樣, 得果幾分鐘興奮但食完已經壞左腦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/nor